Definition: a positive feeling of liking
Example: he had trouble expressing the affection he felt; the child won everyone's heart; the warmness of his welcome made us feel right at home
Synonyms: affectionateness, adj, all, loving, affectionate, fondness, fond, tenderness, tender, heart, warm, hearty, warmness, warmheartedness, warmhearted, philia, noun, Tops, feeling, a, positive, of, liking, he, had, trouble, expressing, the, felt, child, won, everyone, s, his, welcome, made, us, feel, right, at, home
Category: noun.feeling
